WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy B2-M05: Food, health and wellbeing. Learners practise write reports and essays through meals, choices, advice, body, wellness, appointments. The teacher models cleft sentences and emphasis, introduces vocabulary such as food groups, symptoms, healthy habits, advice, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
